init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien has been keeping Damon in a cage and using him as a test subject for experiments.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien has been using Damon for experiments, trying to figure out how the human body works.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien is also trying to figure out how to clone Damon.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The United States government decides to send a robot to the alien's planet to rescue Matt Damon.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The robot lands on the alien's planet and is immediately attacked by the alien.
